                     <code code="42229-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="SPL UNCLASSIFIED SECTION"/>
                     <title>Other information</title>
                     <text>
                        <paragraph>Call your doctor for medical advice about side effects. You may report serious side effects by calling Carwin Pharmaceutical Associates, LLC at 1-844-700-5011.</paragraph>
